OL,3,CSecret evacuation of thousands of
OL,4,CAfghans to UK after MoD data breach
OL,5,Crevealed
OL,7,FThousands of people are being
OL,8,Frelocated to the UK as part of a
OL,9,Fsecret #850 million scheme set up
OL,10,Fafter a personal data leak of Afghans
OL,11,Fwho supported British forces.
OL,13,FA dataset containing the personal
OL,14,Finformation of nearly 19,000 people
OL,15,Fwho applied for the Afghan Relocations
OL,16,Fand Assistance Policy (Arap) was
OL,17,Freleased "in error" in February 2022
OL,18,Fby a defence official.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/16
