OL,5,Crevealed
OL,7,FThe breach resulted in the creation of
OL,8,Fa secret Afghan relocation scheme -
OL,9,Fthe Afghanistan Response Route - in
OL,10,FApril 2024.
OL,12,FThe scheme is understood to have cost
OL,13,Faround #400 million so far, with a
OL,14,Fprojected cost once completed of
OL,15,Faround #850 million.
OL,17,FMillions more is expected to be paid
OL,18,Fin legal costs and compensation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/16
