OL,5,Crevealed
OL,7,FThe Ministry of Defence (MoD) became
OL,8,Faware of the breach over a year after
OL,9,Fthe release, when excerpts of the
OL,10,Fdataset were anonymously posted onto a
OL,11,FFacebook group in August 2023.
OL,13,FAn unprecedented superinjunction
OL,14,Fprevented the media, Parliament and
OL,15,Fpublic from finding out about this
OL,16,Fdata breach for more than 600 days.
OL,18,FThat court order was lifted at the
OL,19,FHigh Court on Tuesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/16
