OL,7,FDetails on the dataset include the the
OL,8,Fnames and contact details of the Arap
OL,9,Fapplicants and names of their family
OL,10,Fmembers.
OL,12,FIt is understood that the unnamed
OL,13,Fofficial had emailed the dataset
OL,14,Foutside of a secure government system
OL,15,Fwhile attempting to verify
OL,16,Finformation, believing the dataset to
OL,17,Fonly have around 150 rows.
OL,19,FHowever, there were more than 33,000
OL,20,Frows of information which were
OL,21,Finadvertently sent.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/16
