OL,7,FIn total, between 80,000 and 100,000
OL,8,Fpeople, including the estimated number
OL,9,Fof family members of the Arap
OL,10,Fapplicants, were affected by the
OL,11,Fbreach and could be at risk of
OL,12,Fharassment, torture or death if the
OL,13,FTaliban obtained their data, judges
OL,14,Fsaid in June 2024.
OL,16,FAround 4,500 people ` made up of 900
OL,17,FArap applicants and approximately
OL,18,F3,600 family members have been brought
OL,19,Fto the UK or are in transit so far
OL,20,Fthrough the Afghanistan Response Route.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/16
