OL,4,CAfghans to UK after MoD data breach
OL,5,Crevealed
OL,7,FA further estimated 600 people and
OL,8,Ftheir relatives are expected to be
OL,9,Frelocated before the scheme closes,
OL,10,Fwith a total of around 6,900 people
OL,11,Fexpected to be relocated by the end of
OL,12,Fthe scheme.
OL,14,FAn unprecedented superinjunction was
OL,15,Fmade at the High Court in September
OL,16,F2023 to reduce the risk of alerting
OL,17,Fthe Taliban to the existence of the
OL,18,Fdata, with the decision to apply for
OL,19,Fan order made by the Conservative's
OL,20,Fthen-Defence Secretary Ben Wallace.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/16
