OL,7,FThe Information Commissioner's Office
OL,8,Fand Metropolitan Police were also
OL,9,Finformed.
OL,11,FA judge had previously ruled in May
OL,12,F2024 that the injunction should be
OL,13,Flifted, saying it was "fundamentally
OL,14,Fobjectionable" that decisions about
OL,15,Fthousands of people's lives and
OL,16,F"enormous sums of public money now
OL,17,Fbeing committed" were being taken in
OL,18,Fsecret.
