OL,7,FIt is expected the cost of seeking and
OL,8,Fmaintaining the superinjunction will
OL,9,Fbe several million pounds.
OL,11,F"Today I'm announcing a change in
OL,12,Fgovernment policy," said Defence
OL,13,FSecretary John Healey as he informed
OL,14,FMPs of the lifting of this
OL,15,Fsuperinjunction and the closure of the
OL,16,Fsecret resettlement scheme.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/16
