OL,7,FAddressing MPs in parliament, Defence
OL,8,FSecretary John Healey formally
OL,9,Fannounced the data breach and the
OL,10,Fclosure of what he termed as the
OL,11,Fprevious government's "secret Afghan
OL,12,Fresettlement route".
OL,14,FHealey said it had been "deeply
OL,15,Funcomfortable to be constrained from
OL,16,Freporting to this house," and that he
OL,17,Fhad been "deeply concerned about the
OL,18,Flack of transparency to parliament and
OL,19,Fto the public."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/16
