OL,7,FHe went on to coinfirm details of the
OL,8,Fincident, saying: "In February 2022,
OL,9,F10 months after the then defence
OL,10,Fsecretary Ben Wallace introduced the
OL,11,FAfghan Relocations and Assistance
OL,12,FPolicy. Six months after the fall of
OL,13,Fkabul. A defence official emailed an
OL,14,FArap case working file outside of
OL,15,Fauthorised government systems."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/16
