OL,7,FAddressing concerns over the security
OL,8,Frisks posed by the secret relocation
OL,9,Fscheme, Healey assured MPs "strict
OL,10,Fnational security cheques" were
OL,11,Fconducted before entry to the UK was
OL,12,Fgranted to these individuals.
OL,14,FThe defence secretary also confirmed
OL,15,Fthe total number of those relocated to
OL,16,Fthe UK under both the publicly known
OL,17,Fscheme and the secret one revealed on
OL,18,FTuesday were counted in the national
OL,19,Fmigration figures.
