OL,7,FHealey concluded offering a "sincere
OL,8,Fapology" to "all those whose
OL,9,Finformation was compromised,"
OL,10,Fpromising the outstanding 600 invites
OL,11,Fmade under this secret scheme to
OL,12,FAfghans still in Afghanistan would be
OL,13,Fhonoured, but that new applications
OL,14,Fwould not be accepted.
OL,16,FHe also reminded MPs of Labour's
OL,17,Fannouncement earlier this month that
OL,18,Fthe public Arap scheme would also be
OL,19,Fdrawn to a close.
