OL,7,FThis was followed by an announcement
OL,8,Fearlier this month that ministers
OL,9,Fagreed to pay those affected
OL,10,Fcompensation to the tune of #4,000,
OL,11,Fpredicting the total cost could fall
OL,12,F"in the region of #1.6million."
OL,14,FIn a written statement earlier this
OL,15,Fmonth, armed forces minister Luke
OL,16,FPollard said he could not, "undo past
OL,17,Fmistakes," but vowed to improve
OL,18,Fpractices in his department going
OL,19,Fforward.
